<figureCitation id="85A12A150159A23DC90BABDBFEDF0D8C" box="[299,328,1235,1259]" captionStart="FIGURES 10 – 13" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1957,1980]" captionTargetBox="[186,1383,193,1931]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[186,1383,193,1932]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 10 – 13. Neoheliothrips sylvanus comb. n. 10 – 12: (10) head and thorax; (11) tergites V – VI; (12) fore wing; (13) Heliothrips haemorrhoidalis fore wing." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/234195/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="579">13</figureCitation>
